Distinguish

" Not to be confused with ... "

*   `{{Distinguish|PAGE1}}` →
    Not to be confused with [PAGE1](/PAGE1).
*   `{{Distinguish|PAGE1|PAGE2|PAGE3|PAGE4}}` →
